values:
What a bore. *pouts* And I was having fun in Seireitai too... <s>Il Forte, you're here by any chance~?</s>

Oh well. Time to find Isshin-chan~! ♥ *skips merrily down the road, despite being naked*

....Kira-kun, did those mushrooms have any sleeping drought? 

And did Byakuya-kun picked up my bathc of cookies yet? I don't even remember giving it to him...
